# Commercial Distribution Compliance

Active when `distribution_tier: commercial` in `.cursor/stack-selection.json` (via `sync-cursor-features.py`).

## License & SDKs

- Proprietary SDKs allowed when documented in ADR and `THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md`
- Play Services, Firebase, and SaaS MCP servers permitted in production path
- Still: no secrets in git; opt-in telemetry only

## Distribution

- App Store, Play Store (non-FOSS track), SaaS, or enterprise channels allowed
- Document store policies and privacy disclosures

## Security

- Gitleaks pre-commit enforced
- CodeQL + Dependabot + Trivy unchanged
- Input validation at all data boundaries

## Cursor Commercial features

- Cloud Agents, Bugbot, Automations — activate via `docs/CURSOR_COMMERCIAL_ACTIVATION.md`
- Never commit live `.cursor/mcp.json`, `.cursor/environment.json`, or API keys

## Android

- See `modules/android/COMMERCIAL.md` for proprietary push/analytics patterns
